FORTRAN 90 code to evaluate the time evolution and the ground sate of atomic BEC using the Gross-Pitaevskii equation. Details of the Crank Nicholson scheme in 
http://eprints.nottingham.ac.uk/11271/1/phd_thesis.pdf


BEC-Crank-Nicolson-3D-ground*.f90 : imaginary time evolution of the 3D GPE to evaluate the ground state
BEC-Crank-Nicolson-3D-timeEvol.f90: Real time evolution of the GPE.

CN_paralelo_ground*.f90   : imaginary time evolution of the GPE using mpi.
CN_paralelo_time_evo*.f90 : Real time evolution of the GPE using mpi.


